What if you lose everything

752
00:38:04,320 --> 00:38:05,559
to my eldest brother here?

753
00:38:06,400 --> 00:38:07,360
Why not?

754
00:38:08,639 --> 00:38:09,599
Don't you want to know

755
00:38:09,599 --> 00:38:10,880
what's in the letter?

756
00:38:11,200 --> 00:38:12,800
Money lost can be retrieved.

757
00:38:14,599 --> 00:38:15,840
I applaud your courage.

758
00:38:16,119 --> 00:38:16,680
Please.

759
