Sure.

761
00:38:19,800 --> 00:38:20,360
Let's go.

762
00:38:32,057 --> 00:38:35,817
♪Life passes by♪

763
00:38:37,097 --> 00:38:44,897
♪In the blink of an eye♪

764
00:38:45,497 --> 00:38:49,257
♪My heart is tied up♪

765
00:38:50,217 --> 00:38:54,297
♪By the unintentional worry♪

766
00:38:58,377 --> 00:39:02,437
♪What does the future hold?♪

767
00:39:03,337 --> 00:39:07,737
♪Hopefully, all wishes will be fulfilled♪

768
00:39:11,397 --> 00:39:15,477
♪What brings us together?♪

769
00:39:16,297 --> 00:39:22,157
♪Why are we going separate ways?♪

770
00:39:49,917 --> 00:39:55,797
♪I can never express love
and hate in words♪

771
00:39:55,797 --> 00:40:02,837
♪Going through all the winters in our lives♪

772
00:40:02,837 --> 00:40:08,557
♪Disposing of the unfulfilled wishes♪

773
00:40:08,557 --> 00:40:15,077
♪And keeping them all to myself♪

774
00:40:16,617 --> 00:40:22,077
♪Love only lasts so briefly♪

775
00:40:22,617 --> 00:40:28,677
♪Who do I waste my time for?♪

776
00:40:29,417 --> 00:40:34,677
♪Life is already full of debts♪

777
00:40:35,857 --> 00:40:42,077
♪So let's not dwell on the little time we have♪


